Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[crunching]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always taking\Nsuch good care of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gees, Sayu, you're all grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[caller] Look, about trading the director\Nin exchange for the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's been canceled.\N-[all] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The new deal is this:\NThe notebook for Sayu Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to L.A. by yourself in two days\Nand bring the notebook with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to meet you at last,\NL Number Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I am at the center of the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can address me as N.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N? Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, this strange feeling, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,IMPATIENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] N?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I feel like I'm talking to L?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] I told you that we wouldn't rely on L.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's a bit of an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI and the CIA have explicitly asked\Nthat I head up their investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we are outraged by the recent murder\Nof the director of the NPA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel something must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After revealing the information,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe there's a possibility\Nthat solving this case
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,could lead to the arrest of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, I'm willing to lend you\Nmy full support.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] "Lead to the arrest of Kira"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] Is there a problem, L?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that following the death\Nof Takimura,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy Director Yagami's daughter\Nwas kidnapped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and we believe the same person\Nis behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's arranged for a trade in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] A trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl in exchange for the notebook,\NI assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a team on standby in L.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, they'll be working\Non a need-to-know basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My cell can monitor the city\Nvia satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, I'll let you have\Nfull authority on this, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[N hangs up]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.\NIt means we're taking the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's all this about the Americans\Nnot trusting L anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, is it really safe to leave this case\Nin the hands of a fake L?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had any success\Nin catching Kira so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that.\NThat's why it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It means there'll be an opportunity\Nto take advantage of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, saving people’s lives\Nis important,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but as the SPK,\Nour primary goal is very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll work to get the notebook\Nand capture Kira once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Soichiro] Light…\N-Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, I don't care\Nif it costs me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just save Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking like that, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You might have made your peace\Nwith the idea of dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but have you ever thought\Nabout how painful it would be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for everyone else you leave behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never be able to forgive you\Nif you ended up dying in front of Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's true that you might\Nlose contact with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that happens and you have to make\Na split-second decision by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,then I want you to do whatever's necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure both you and Sayu\Nget out of this alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You really want me\Nto go to Los Angeles with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a chance I might need\Nto use your eyes this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want to have you close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Light! You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh,\NI'd better start packing right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, which one should I bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, which do you like? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[water pouring]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If things go badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have to kill Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[bird chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Dad, I'll fly to L.A. ahead of you\Nand make preparations for the handover.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ide and the others\Nshould arrive shortly after,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but to be safe, we should all arrive\Non separate flights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aizawa, I want you\Nto tail my father closely
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and get on the same plane as him,\Njust in case something goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get a haircut\Nso they won't recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[planes flying overhead]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Okay everyone,\NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? One of the kidnappers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to board flight SE333.\NI have your tickets with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It leaves from Gate 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has intercepted him at Narita!\NShould I arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Calm down, Mr. Aizawa.\NDon't make any sudden moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand your concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but arresting him now\Nwill accomplish nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your distance\Nand don't lose sight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Oh, damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're boarding a different flight\Nthan originally planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them at the gate\Nthat I'm a police officer and--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just blow your cover\Nand the operation would be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you find out\Nwhere the flight's headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's going to L.A. too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they have somehow arranged\Nfor another plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[plane engines roaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[air traffic control] Flight SE333?\NFlight SE333, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you copy?\NYou have strayed from your flight path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[pilot] This is Flight SE333,\NI read you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I assure you, everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[air traffic control] What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to tell me\Nwhat's going on up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a hijacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're simply making a detour\Nand a quick stop to drop off a passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[pilot] You can track us by radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you attempt\Nto call the authorities
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to interfere with our course,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not hesitate to crash the plane\Nand take all the passengers with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Light… I mean, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Deputy Director's flight\Nhas just changed direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A passenger's going to be\Ndropped off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I already checked today's flight crew\Nand passenger lists ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No one on board was suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot's a veteran\Nof over fifteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The co-pilot checks out clean too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the kidnappers are powerful enough\Nto influence these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it looks like I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[dialing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, this is L. Get me N.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Director] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] N, I'm sure you're aware\Nof our current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you notify the airlines,\Npolice, and military on your end
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,not to take any action yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he thinking?\NI never realized he was this unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, L, agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll locate the landing site
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep surveillance over the area\Nusing our satellite video feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything else we can do,\Ndon't hesitate to let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Yagami, right now,\Nyou're the only one who can hear my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who kidnapped your daughter,\Nbut don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest\Nin your daughter's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or yours, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing I want\Nand you know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all you have to do\Nis follow my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, no one has to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared things so that both of us\Ncan walk away satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Play along and there'll be no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] I'm going to give the notebook\Nto some criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in exchange for my daughter's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\Nwhat's the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As a police officer, as a human being,\Nand as a parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[plane engines roaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[plane engines shutting down]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[machines beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,L, we've been able to use\Nour satellite cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to pinpoint where the plane has landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you a direct video feed\Nof what we're currently seeing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How will he make the exchange\Nin a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[mechanical whirring]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] You see the entrance,\Ndon't you, Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, isn't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[mechanical whirring]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. An underground facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The kidnapper must've predicted\Nthat we'd be watching him by satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That means there's no way\Nto keep an eye on Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gun cocks]\N-[Soichiro gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshots]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] The glass is bulletproof,\Nunderstand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This place used to belong\Nto a crime syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They used to make trades just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made a few modifications as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Slide the notebook through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that's done, I'll release the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll both step back\Nand spin the glass door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The notebook will end up on my side,\Nand the girl on yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you don't agree to this trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot your daughter\Nthrough this opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] L, do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't seriously think\Nthat handing the notebook over
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to someone you don't know\Nis a good idea, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Y462, proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,First, open the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and insert it halfway into the slot\Nin the glass door on your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it!\NIt's setback after setback.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've only just arrived in the US,\Nso I'm not in any position
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to start giving orders\Nto the American police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[heavy breathing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the notebook's going be--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong? You look kinda--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, just shut up\Nand do what I told you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Look, I need you to keep killing\NJapanese criminals so just do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is obviously investigating Kira\Nand he won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If the killings are delayed,\Nwe're in trouble. Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay. But who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Just get on with it, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking out your anger on her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] I can still make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate, is my only option...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Now then, I'll test the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] Test it?\NYou're gonna kill someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't make the trade\Nwithout making sure it's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want\Nto see your daughter die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No one but the police\Nknows about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sayu dies,\NI can't blame her death on Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Argh!\N-[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You okay, Miller?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that's what you get\Nwhen you steal from me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and sell goods behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a worthless idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time he's been useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Y462, the target is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the notebook\Nis genuine after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let it go. We'll make the exchange\Nfor your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they actually made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mason] The suspect is headed\Nfor a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on our intel, that's his only method\Nof transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So this means we can be absolutely certain\Nthat the notebook has been exchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know what they're planning\Nto do beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,N, I need you to maintain surveillance\Nof that helicopter until it lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose sight of it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to think\Nthat's quite an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, we'll do what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] I'm sorry.\NI'm afraid we've been tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] A missile?\N-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] You won't be able that with radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the notebook on that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[rocket blasting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] The missile's been launched!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The missile or the helicopter? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[rotors whirring]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, I'm sure you were watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I did everything you asked me to,\Njust like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw that. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is gonna wipe out\Nall those past screw-ups of mine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, wiped out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[bleeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, the helicopter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, it means the notebook\Nis definitely on the missile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We can't track it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost the signal.\NIt could be anywhere now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[machines bleeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts in frustration]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[splashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be difficult\Nto retrieve the missile
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,once it lands in a deserted area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have already laid out\Nthe flight plan accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be getting his hands\Non the notebook any moment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he does, I have a good idea\Nof what he'll do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[dice rolling on the floor]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning in pain]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelping and choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-"Got" you?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The majority of the SPK's members\Nhave just been killed by the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,L, you were the one who handed over\Nthe notebook without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your people were totally helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,N, are you saying\Nif you were in command,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have handed it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, considering their preparations,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it would have been impossible\Nto avoid this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really no point in us quarreling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] I propose we work together\Nand share the information we know so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, I should admit\Nthat I have a very good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of who the culprit behind this might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] I suspect the person who arranged\Nthe kidnapping and the trade
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is someone who goes by the name "Mello."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Mello? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] I don't have his photograph\Nand I don't know his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know about him\Nis that four years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,he was living at an orphanage\Nlocated in Winchester, England,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,known as Wammy's House.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wammy's House?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the place Watari established.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[N] I believe Mello\Nis playing a game with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to see which of us\Nwill be the first to take down Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The final challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Armo Justin…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Armonia Justin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, um, I've got a little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the king to report\Nthat I lost my notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but after I described it to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the old man said\Nthat Ryuk said it was his,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he had dropped it and took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do\Nto get it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you have no choice\Nbut to find Ryuk and ask him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess I have\Nto go to the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]